    "ChatEval [21] uses debater agents in an LLM-powered MAS for text evaluation, achieving enhanced accuracy and depth over traditional methods and single agent setups.",
    "MetaGPT [22], a metaprogramming framework, enhances multi-agent collaboration using an assembly line approach for software engineering tasks.These works demonstrate advanced multi-agent interactions, realistic behavior simulation, and task efficiency, which can enhance adaptability, coordination, and advanced natural language processing capabilities in manufacturing.",
